	"FLASHBACKS" => "<p>During exposure to something that reminds XXXXcharnameXXXX  of your traumatic event, XXXXcharnameXXXX  immediately flash back to your traumatic event. During your flashback, XXXXcharnameXXXX  are not interacting with the present in any meaningful way. Everything is for XXXXcharnameXXXX  as it was - which means when XXXXcharnameXXXX  come out of your flashback, XXXXcharnameXXXX  could be in a Bad Situation. The duration is subjective.</p>",

