	"INSANITIY (Herediatary)" => "<p>Your family tree doesn&#39;t branch much, yet theres a whole lot of <em>  Forks</em>  he&#39;ll always being a victim to his own genetics. While it hasn&#39;t been a problem for Brainiac 5 in full, he is descended from a line of highly unstable, and often psychopathic, villains. It shows in little ways, such as his mood swings, and lack of ability to think of the consequences of his own actions, but this time bomb lays within him waiting to be set off.</p>",

