	"MUTE" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX  is physically unable to speak, and must communicate through writing or sign language (or perhaps telepathy).</p>",

	"NAIVE" => "<p>From the French Naivete: XXXXcharnameXXXX  lacks a certain amount of experience and understanding when dealing with the day-today nuances of everyday life and events. As such <em> he/she</em>  is given to feeling confused and or frustrated during times of crisis which may cause XXXXcharnameXXXX  to over react to in an erratic, rash or violent manner. Additionally <em> LN</em>  lack of sophistication may cause XXXXcharnameXXXX  to fall victim to the manipulations of others due to lack of knowing and or understanding of <world> customs. by a pretty face.</p>",

	"NARCOLEPSY" => "<p>Even at very inconvenient times, XXXXcharnameXXXX  have difficulty avoiding sleep. Every CON x2 + 6 minutes, XXXXcharnameXXXX  must make a CON test (with mods as the Storyteller decides) to stay awake if XXXXcharnameXXXX  are doing something that does not require XXXXcharnameXXXX  to be attentive or active, such as guard duty, driving for a long time, or listening to a boring lecture.</p>",

	"NATURAL BORN KILLER" => "<p>Instead of getting your violent tendencies through a Bloodline, your darkness is inborn; You are a republician.</p>
