	"NERVOUS CONDITION" => "<p>XXXXcharnameXXXX  has been scarred by trauma. The damage manifests as physical ailments that impact your life daily. XXXXcharnameXXXX  suffer nervous tension and muscle tremors that affect routine tasts. XXXXcharnameXXXX  hands and feet tremble almost constantly, and shake even faster when XXXXcharnameXXXX  experience stress which may cause your character to become wreckless or immobilized by fear.</p>",

