	"OBESSESSION -</span>qa Oh My God Pam Grier is hot! - more of a description to come.</p>",

	"OBESSIVE COMPULSIVE DISORDER" => "<p>Guilt, trauma, and inner conflict forces to focus attention on repetitive behavior and actions. Obsession relates to the desire to control the environnment - keeping clean, keeping an area silent, or keeping away undesirables. Compulsions are actions or a set of actions that individuals do to soothe their anxiety: placing everything In Order, checking their gun to make sure it is loaded, or praying every few hours.</p>",

